## API Endpoints (base: `/api`)
### Categories
- POST `/api/categories` â€” create category
- GET `/api/categories` â€” list categories
- GET `/api/categories/:idOrName` â€” get category by id or name (includes subcategories & direct items)
- PUT `/api/categories/:id` â€” update category

### Subcategories
- POST `/api/subcategories/category/:categoryId` â€” create subcategory for category
- GET `/api/subcategories` â€” list all subcategories
- GET `/api/subcategories/category/:categoryId` â€” list subcategories under category
- GET `/api/subcategories/:idOrName` â€” get subcategory by id or name (includes items)
- PUT `/api/subcategories/:id` â€” update subcategory

### Items
- POST `/api/items/category/:categoryId` â€” create item under category (optional `?subCategoryId=...`)
- GET `/api/items` â€” list all items
- GET `/api/items/category/:categoryId` â€” list items under category
- GET `/api/items/subCategory/:subCategoryId` â€” list items under subcategory
- GET `/api/items/:idOrName` â€” get item by id or name
- PUT `/api/items/id/:id` â€” update item
- GET `/api/items/search?q=term` â€” search items by name


## âœ… Setup (local)

1. Clone repo:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/NarenderDhariwal10/menu_managementBackend
   cd menu_managementBackend
   ```
2. Install Dependencies:
   ```bash
   npm install
   ```
3. Create .env
    ```bash
    PORT=
    MONGO_URI=
    ```
4. Run server:
   ```bash
   npm start
   ```
